---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="About FlowHat Blog"
	pubDate={new Date('April 12 2026')}
>
	<p>
		FlowHat Blog is a git-backed publication focused on LLMs, agents, coding tools, and practical
		workflows.
	</p>

	<p>
		The goal is simple: publish useful posts that do more than summarize announcements. Each post
		should add evaluation, synthesis, or practical guidance that helps someone actually use the tools.
	</p>

	<p>
		The scope is intentionally narrow for now. Models, agent products, coding agents, subagents,
		multi-agent workflows, and the operational details around using them well.
	</p>
</Layout>
